--------------------------------------------------------------------
Service framework integrations
--------------------------------------------------------------------

This product interacts with — but does not bundle — the following
service frameworks at runtime via their CLI surfaces:

* macOS launchd (Apple Inc., proprietary; documented APIs)
* Linux systemd (LGPL-2.1+, not linked, invoked as user-mode service)
* OpenClaw (https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw)
* Claude Code CLI (Anthropic)

Detection and version-probing of these tools is read-only and uses
their published CLI contracts; no source from these projects is
incorporated.
